	<div class="home_hero_title_and_intro_container">
		<h3 class="home_hero_title">
			 
			<span> Our Standards </span>
			 		</h3>
		<h1 class="home_hero_intro">We uphold the highest standards of ethical and professional journalism through our Editorial Code, when we work with advertising partners, and in the areas of reader trust, privacy and user experience.</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="home_hero_grid">
		<img
			src="https://images.prismic.io/ip-about-us/b64b97db-5494-44cf-97a6-6eccf5fe3db1_Our+Standards.jpg?auto&#x3D;compress,format"
